Diffium demo playground

This file exists so you can quickly demo Diffium’s live watcher.

Try this:
- Edit this file: change a word, add a line, or delete a line.
- In another terminal, run: go run ./cmd/diffium watch
- Watch the left pane update and the right pane show a side‑by‑side diff.
- Press c to open the commit overlay and walk through the wizard.

Sample text to edit below:

Line A: The quick brown fox
Line B: jumps over the lazy dog
Line C: end of demo

